<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>COMM&#160;416.  Conflict and Communication.  3 or 4 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Students learn to manage and resolve conflict in business, governmental, and community settings. Practical analysis of interpersonal and group conflict cases. Course Information: 3 undergraduate hours. 4 graduate hours. Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=COMM%20301" title="COMM&#160;301" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'COMM 301');">COMM&#160;301</a>.<br />
