</div><div class="courseblock">
<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>COMM&#160;433.  Mobile Media and the City.  3 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Relationship between contemporary technologies - new media, urban screens, mobile and wireless technologies, ubiquitous computing - and cities. Foundational theory on mobile media and communication. Course Information: Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=COMM%20301" title="COMM&#160;301" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'COMM 301');">COMM&#160;301</a>.<br />
