Classic and current research. Models that examine organizational communication; assessment of organizational problems and conduct of problem-solving research. Course Information: Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=COMM%20306" title="COMM&#160;306" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'COMM 306');">COMM&#160;306</a> and <a href="/search/?P=COMM%20500" title="COMM&#160;500" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'COMM 500');">COMM&#160;500</a>; or consent of the instructor.<br />
