<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>COMM&#160;506.  Cross-Cultural Communication.  4 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Analysis of different theoretical approaches to cross-cultural communication (sociolinguistic, attributional); contrastive analysis of Western and non-Western cultural systems (interactional etiquette, discourse rules). Course Information: Same as <a href="/search/?P=LING%20506" title="LING&#160;506" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'LING 506');">LING&#160;506</a>.<br />
