<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>COMM&#160;525.  Approaches to Rhetorical Criticism.  4 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Contemporary approaches to rhetorical criticism. Each offering focuses upon the distinctive contributions of specified rhetoricians to the theory and practice of rhetorical criticism. Course Information: May be repeated to a maximum of 12 hours. Prerequisite(s): COMM 410.<br />
</p>
