<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>COMM&#160;534.  Mass Communication Theory.  4 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Introduction to major theories of mass communication: their social history and substantive claims; distinction between mass mediated and other forms of communication, implications of distinction.<br />
</p>
</div><div class="courseblock">
