<p class="courseblockdesc">
Provides students with a survey of methods, theory and research in language and discourse processing.  Course Information: Same as <a href="/search/?P=PSCH%20554" title="PSCH&#160;554" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'PSCH 554');">PSCH&#160;554</a> and <a href="/search/?P=LING%20554" title="LING&#160;554" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'LING 554');">LING&#160;554</a>. Prerequisite(s): Graduate standing or consent of the instructor.<br />
