</div><div class="courseblock">
<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>COMM&#160;567.  Topics in Political Communication.  4 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Intensive study of selected aspects; organizational communication in public institutions, urban political communication patterns, communication elites. Independent research using a variety of community research techniques. Course Information: Same as <a href="/search/?P=PA%20567" title="PA&#160;567" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'PA 567');">PA&#160;567</a> and <a href="/search/?P=POLS%20567" title="POLS&#160;567" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'POLS 567');">POLS&#160;567</a>. Prerequisite(s): Consent of the instructor.<br />
