<p class="courseblockdesc">
Conceptual approaches to technology, with special emphasis on communication technologies. Emphasis on the application of values, beliefs, and thoughts related to the interplay of technology and society. Course Information: Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=COMM%20504" title="COMM&#160;504" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'COMM 504');">COMM&#160;504</a>.<br />
</p>
</div><div class="courseblock">
<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>COMM&#160;580.  Qualitative Methods in Communication.  4 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Qualitative methods course analyzing language and culture patterns. Course Information: Same as <a href="/search/?P=LING%20582" title="LING&#160;582" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'LING 582');">LING&#160;582</a>. Prerequisite(s):  <a href="/search/?P=COMM%20501" title="COMM&#160;501" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'COMM 501');">COMM&#160;501</a> or consent of the instructor.<br />
