</div><div class="courseblock">
<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>COMM&#160;594.  Advanced Special Topics in Communication.  1-4 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Student may register for more than one section per term. Advanced topics in communication theory and research. Subject matter varies. Course Information: May be repeated. Students may register in more than one section per term. Prerequisite(s): Consent of the instructor.<br />
</p>
