<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>COMM&#160;599.  Dissertation Research.  0-16 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Under guidance of an advisor and committee, the student conducts research on the topic of the doctoral dissertation. Course Information: Satisfactory/Unsatisfactory grading only. May be repeated. Students may register for more than one section per term. Prerequisite(s): Consent of the instructor.<br />
</p>
